NAVY PIER lagged early, raced three-wide through the turn, angled in with a furlong to run and was up for the place. SILENT DECLARATION chased the leaders from the inside, angled out into the lane, drifted out in mid-stretch to bump rival and gave way. KAI'S STATEMENT disputed the pace with the winner while racing three-wide, was bumped by SILENT DECLARATION in mid-stretch while retreating and continued to give way. IMISSBAYMEADOWS raced off the pacesetters early, moved four-wide through the turn and weakened. THE STEWARDS CONDUCTED AN INQUIRY CONCERNING THE BUMPING OF KAI'S STATEMENT IN MID-STRETCH AND AFTER REVIEWING THE FILMS CONCLUDED THAT SILENT DECLARATION HAD DRIFTED IN TO BUMP THAT RIVAL AND WAS DISQUALIFIED FROM FIFTH AND PLACED SIXTH.
